Secrets: Whoever hides knowledge will be punished","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is asked about knowledge and he conceals it, Allah will clothe him with a bridle of fire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2649 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/05\/warning-seek-knowledge-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":18222,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Warning to study Islam for worldly reasons","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks knowledge to impress the scholars, to argue with the foolish, or to attract the attention of people, Allah will admit him into Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2654 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/23\/dust-jihad-dukhan-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":18222,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Dust in jihad and smoke of Hell never combine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man who weeps from the fear of Allah will never enter Hellfire, unless milk could return to its udder. The dust in the way of Allah will never combine with the smoke of Hell.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28831,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/tafsir-quran-ignorance\/","url_meta":{"origin":18222,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: Warning not to interpret Quran without knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever speaks on the Quran without knowledge, let him take his seat in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2950 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/dunya-cursed-dhikr-ilm\/","url_meta":{"origin":18222,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: World is cursed except for prayer, knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIs not the world cursed and everything in it? Except for the remembrance of Allah and what facilitates it, the scholar or the student.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2322 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5697,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/30\/talab-ilm-wajib-faridah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18222,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Learning: Seeking knowledge an obligation on every Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeeking knowledge is an obligation upon every Muslim.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 224 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\